joelib2.io.types
Class MDLSD

java.lang.Object
  joelib2.io.types.MDLSD
All Implemented Interfaces:
MoleculeFileExport, MoleculeFileImport, MoleculeFileIO, PropertyWriter
public class MDLSD
extends Object
implements MoleculeFileIO, PropertyWriter

Reader/Writer for SDF files. For speeding up descriptor molecule files have a look at the ResultFactory.
